            <title>[JDK-8191565] Last-ditch Full GC should also move humongous objects</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8191565</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>To avoid the VM going OOM due to region fragmentation with humongous object allocations if there is still plenty of space available, the &amp;quot;last-ditch&amp;quot; full gc should also move humongous objects.</description>
