                            <comment id="14137945" author="shade" created="Wed, 6 Dec 2017 10:37:09 -0800"  >FTR, we have implemented the similar strategy in Shenandoah recently: &lt;a href=&quot;http://mail.openjdk.java.net/pipermail/shenandoah-dev/2017-December/004398.html&quot;&gt;http://mail.openjdk.java.net/pipermail/shenandoah-dev/2017-December/004398.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
